channel.description:
Hello there, these are our friends models so dont flame or say THESE SUCK or Spam. My friends name is victor so when i refer to victor i mean him Below here i will be showing pictures of our first models and who they are made by
Victor's Outlined Sketch [IMG]http://i32.tinypic.com/n35krr.jpg[/img]
Victor's Weapon [IMG]http://i32.tinypic.com/2z6f3ph.jpg[/img]
My Outlined Sketch [IMG]http://i25.tinypic.com/2q204jl.jpg[/img]
My Outlined Sketch up close part 1. [IMG]http://i26.tinypic.com/11r7r75.jpg[/img]
My Outlined Sketch up close part 2. [IMG]http://i29.tinypic.com/19b6dd.jpg[/img]
My Outlined Sketch up close part 3. [IMG]http://i31.tinypic.com/2ef7p1y.jpg[/img]
My weapon [IMG]http://i32.tinypic.com/mcgl76.jpg[/img]
My Weapon Finished [IMG]http://i28.tinypic.com/28wf0xz.jpg[/img]
Victors upcoming Weapon [IMG]http://i28.tinypic.com/2mbpzp.jpg[/img]
I hope you liked our first models as much we did also please reply if you liked the yellow or silverish gray version of my weapon.
Thnx bye - Zanakinz
